docs.text:
Field Type Required Description <code>player</code> string Yes The name of the player initiating the chat. Used for player-specific memory. <code>message</code> string Yes The message content from the player. <code>model</code> string No The specific AI model to use for this request. If omitted, the default model from <code>config.yml</code> is used. <p>Example JSON Body:</p> <pre><code>{
  "player": "Steve",
  "message": "What are the ingredients for a cake?",
  "model": "google/gemini-pro"
}
</code></pre>
